== 評論和争议 ==
2010年3月，Kit Kat因有使用[[棕榈油|棕榈油]]被成为[[绿色和平|绿色和平组织]]抵制的目标，其環境組織聲稱使用棕欖油會導致印度尼西亞[[紅毛猩猩|紅毛猩猩]]的森林棲息地遭到破壞<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/scott-poynton/dancing-with-devils_b_837442.html|title=Dancing With Devils|last=Poynton|first=Scott|work=[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]|publisher=[[AOL|AOL]]|location=New York|date=2011-03-18|accessdate=2013-05-05|archive-date=2016-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160121142124/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/scott-poynton/dancing-with-devils_b_837442.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 有一個綠色組織的Youtube影片因在網路上[[網路爆紅短片|爆紅]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2010/WORLD/asiapcf/03/19/indonesia.rainforests.orangutan.nestle/index.html?_s=PM:WORLD|title=Greenpeace, Nestlé in battle over Kit Kat viral|last=Armstrong|first=Paul|work=cnn.com|publisher=[[CNN|Cable News Network]]|date=2013-03-02|accessdate=2013-05-05|archive-date=2018-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180509075607/http://www.cnn.com/2010/WORLD/asiapcf/03/19/indonesia.rainforests.orangutan.nestle/index.html?_s=PM:WORLD|dead-url=no}}</ref>造成雀巢宣布與The Forest Trust建立合作夥伴關係，以製定“負責任的採購指南”，並確保其產品沒有留下森林破壞的足跡。他們的目標是能在2015年實現完全可持續採集棕櫚油的方法。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nestle.com/Media/Statements/Pages/Update-on-deforestation-and-palm-oil.aspx|title=Nestlé committed to traceable sustainable palm oil to ensure no-deforestation|publisher=[[Nestlé|Nestlé]]|date=2012-10-30|accessdate=2013-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102152229/http://www.nestle.com/Media/Statements/Pages/Update-on-deforestation-and-palm-oil.aspx|archive-date=2014-11-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。雀巢表示，2017年購買的棕櫚油中有58％是來自可靠的來源<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nestle.com/csv/raw-materials/palm-oil|title=Palm oil|publisher=[[Nestlé|Nestlé]]|date=2018|accessdate=2018-11-11|archive-date=2018-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181111215345/https://www.nestle.com/csv/raw-materials/palm-oil|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

Kit Kat在北美市场上，在牛奶巧克力使用PGPR （polyol polyricinoleate, E476, 又名 Palsgaard PGPR 4150）成分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thehersheycompany.com/brands/kit-kat-wafer-bars/milk-chocolate.aspx?cat=icon|title=KIT KAT Milk Chocolate|access-date=2015-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150217235503/http://www.thehersheycompany.com/brands/kit-kat-wafer-bars/milk-chocolate.aspx?cat=icon|archive-date=2015-02-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>；PGPR可以减少[[可可脂|可可脂]]的用量，也可以作为[[乳化剂|乳化剂]]。美国食品和药物管理局（FDA）已经确定，每公斤体重7.5毫克的钠对人体是安全的。但在更高剂量下，肝脏和肾脏會增大<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fda.gov/downloads/food/ingredientspackaginglabeling/gras/noticeinventory/ucm356269.pdf |title=GRAS Notice 000466: polyricinoleic acid |format=PDF |date= |accessdate=2016-07-09 |archive-date=2017-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170607005320/https://www.fda.gov/downloads/Food/IngredientsPackagingLabeling/GRAS/NoticeInventory/UCM356269.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

